and what the left....</i>

357
00:37:39,175 --> 00:37:44,180
<i>--a hearty meal for the hungry bird
who lived to hunt another day.</i>

358
00:38:03,700 --> 00:38:08,830
<i>--thirteen pounds
and a wingspan of nearly 7 feet.</i>

359
00:38:23,928 --> 00:38:27,057
